abstract: An environmental think tank says turning plant matter into liquid fuel or electricity is so inefficient that the approach is unlikely ever to supply a substantial fraction of global energy demand.
snippet: An environmental think tank says turning plant matter into liquid fuel or electricity is so inefficient that the approach is unlikely ever to supply a substantial fraction of global energy demand.
lead_paragraph: Western governments have made a wrong turn in energy policy by supporting the large-scale conversion of plants into fuel and should reconsider that strategy, according to a new report from a prominent environmental think tank.

abstract: The company doesn’t tend to play it safe with design, and the new Murano has elements, like its flowing brightwork, that are bold and refreshing.
snippet: The company doesn’t tend to play it safe with design, and the new Murano has elements, like its flowing brightwork, that are bold and refreshing.
lead_paragraph: LEAF, Juke, Quest and Cube are proof that Nissan doesn’t play it safe with design. This could be because of its alliance with the French automaker Renault. If not, the French curves Nissan uses must come directly from the mother country.
headline_main: Video Review: The 2015 Nissan Murano, Dressed Up and Looking Good

abstract: The Consumer Financial Protection Bureau said that more than 100 former Wells Fargo loan officers and half a dozen from JPMorgan accepted kickbacks. The banks agreed to pay about $36 million.
snippet: The Consumer Financial Protection Bureau said that more than 100 former Wells Fargo loan officers and half a dozen from JPMorgan accepted kickbacks. The banks agreed to pay about $36 million.
lead_paragraph: More than 100 former Wells Fargo loan officers accepted kickbacks – including one former employee’s wife who collected tens of thousands of dollars in payments – as part of a scheme to steer business to a now defunct title insurance company, a federal regulator said on Thursday.

abstract: Tom Steyer, a billionaire environmentalist, bowed out of the race to succeed Senator Barbara Boxer, leaving the California attorney general, Kamala D. Harris, as the main candidate.
snippet: Tom Steyer, a billionaire environmentalist, bowed out of the race to succeed Senator Barbara Boxer, leaving the California attorney general, Kamala D. Harris, as the main candidate.
lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES — The supposedly crowded race to succeed Senator Barbara Boxer, the California Democrat who is not seeking re-election in 2016, just became less crowded.

headline_main: Race for Boxer’s Senate Seat Loses a High-Profile Hopeful
headline_print_headline: Race for Boxer’s Senate Seat Loses a High-Profile Hopeful

abstract: Tom Steyer, the billionaire environmentalist, said he would not run for the California Senate seat being vacated by Barbara Boxer.
snippet: Tom Steyer, the billionaire environmentalist, said he would not run for the California Senate seat being vacated by Barbara Boxer.
lead_paragraph: Cross another name off the list of potential Senate candidates in California.
headline_main: Steyer Stands Down on California Senate Run

abstract: President Obama will deliver his State of the Union address Tuesday night, outlining his agenda in front of a joint session of Congress fully controlled by Republicans for the first time in his presidency.

abstract: Many cars in this segment now offer luxuries like keyless ignition, rear-view cameras and heated leather seats. Don’t look for them in the Yaris.
snippet: Many cars in this segment now offer luxuries like keyless ignition, rear-view cameras and heated leather seats. Don’t look for them in the Yaris.
lead_paragraph: AUTOMOTIVE engineers say the most difficult vehicle to produce is a budget subcompact. Certainly, luxury cars stuffed with tech are complex projects. But building a car that’s compelling, affordable, comfortable and — here’s the tricky part — profitable? That’s a black art of the highest order.

abstract: Romaine Sweat may be struggling to raise four children on his own, but he swells with happiness when he talks about their accomplishments.
snippet: Romaine Sweat may be struggling to raise four children on his own, but he swells with happiness when he talks about their accomplishments.
lead_paragraph: Along with all the demands and unpredictability of single fatherhood comes something else: all of the credit. And Romaine Sweat, 37, could not be prouder to take it.

headline_main: Single Father Embraces His Role With Pride
headline_print_headline: Single Father Embraces His Role With Pride

abstract: The attorney general, Kamala D. Harris, plans to run for the Senate seat opening up with Barbara Boxer’s retirement. Tom Steyer, the billionaire environmentalist, said he was also considering a run.
snippet: The attorney general, Kamala D. Harris, plans to run for the Senate seat opening up with Barbara Boxer’s retirement. Tom Steyer, the billionaire environmentalist, said he was also considering a run.
lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES — No exploratory committees here: Kamala D. Harris, the California attorney general, announced on Tuesday that she was running for the Senate seat that is opening up with Barbara Boxer’s retirement.

headline_main: One Democrat Announces While Others Ponder a Race for the Senate in California
headline_print_headline: One Democrat Announces While Others Ponder a Race for the Senate in California

abstract: Kamala Harris, the California attorney general, announced on Tuesday she is running for the Senate seat that is opening up with Barbara Boxer’s retirement at the end of the year.
snippet: Kamala Harris, the California attorney general, announced on Tuesday she is running for the Senate seat that is opening up with Barbara Boxer’s retirement at the end of the year.
lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES — No exploratory committees here. Kamala D. Harris, the California attorney general, announced on Tuesday that she was running for the Senate seat that is opening up with Barbara Boxer’s impending retirement.
